Template: llm-systems-agent/manager-url
Type: string
Description: Manager URL:
 Full URL, with port, of the LLM Systems Manager this agent reports to,
 e.g. http://192.0.2.10:5000. A bare host or IP is completed to
 http://<host>:5000. Leave blank to set it later in
 /opt/llm-systems-agent/agent_config.yaml.

Template: llm-systems-agent/alarm-engine-url
Type: string
Description: Alarm engine URL:
 Leave blank to derive it from the manager host (port 8081). A bare
 host or IP is completed to http://<host>:8081.

Template: llm-systems-agent/url-invalid
Type: error
Description: Invalid URL
 "${value}" is not a usable URL. Enter http[s]://host[:port], a bare
 host/IP (the default port is filled in), or leave the field blank.
